# Change & Release Checklist

## Every code change
- `CHANGELOG.md` — add entry under `[Unreleased]`
- Add/update tests for changed behavior
- Keep Frankie/Abridge out of core (`src/`)

There is intentionally no `TODO.md`. See `AGENTS.md` for the source-of-truth file list.

## Version bump (before tagging)
- `package.json` — `version`
- `src/version.ts` — `RELAY_VERSION` constant (cli + mcp + update read it)
- `CHANGELOG.md` — move `[Unreleased]` to new `[x.y.z]` section, update compare links
- Tag: `git tag v0.x.y && git push origin v0.x.y` (triggers binary release)
- Update `yoreai/homebrew-tap` formula URL + sha256 after release assets exist
